## ~/.tigrc
## tig Personal Preference File @tearoom6

## Settings
# commits
set commit-order = topo
# status
set status-show-untracked-files = yes

## Key Bindings
# move
bind generic g move-first-line
bind generic G move-last-line
# checkout
bind refs n !git checkout -b %(prompt Enter branch name:) %(branch)
# remove
bind status D !@?rm %(file)

